show.description: A brilliant medical school hopeful's life shatters when she returns home to find her parents brutally murdered under mysterious circumstances. Abandoning her promising future, she plunges into a personal investigation that reveals her seemingly peaceful hometown harbors dark, dangerous secrets. As she unravels the truth behind the killings, she discovers that finding justice might cost her everything—including her own life.
